{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idcacf2122-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s5504"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5504"},"text":"§ 5504.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Model intermodal transportation plans","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcacf2123-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s5504/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Grants","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Transportation shall make grants to States to develop model State intermodal transportation plans that are consistent with the policy set forth in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t49/s302/e"},"text":"section 302(e) of this title","children":[],"tail":". The model plans shall include systems for collecting data related to intermodal transportation."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcacf2124-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s5504/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Distribution","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall award grants to States under this section that represent a variety of geographic regions and transportation needs, patterns, and modes.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcacf2125-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s5504/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Plan Submission","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"As a condition to a State receiving a grant under this section, the Secretary shall require that the State provide assurances that the State will submit to the Secretary a State intermodal transportation plan not later than 18 months after the date of receipt of the grant.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcacf2126-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s5504/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Grant Amounts","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall reserve, from amounts deducted under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t23/s104/a"},"text":"section 104(a) of title 23","children":[],"tail":", $3,000,000 to make grants under this section. The total amount that a State may receive in grants under this section may not be more than $500,000."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idcacf2127-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/272/s1/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–272, § 1(d)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-07-05"},"text":"July 5, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/850"},"text":"108 Stat. 850","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idcacf2128-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"historicalAndRevision","id":"idcacf2129-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:table","attrib":{"width":"50%","id":"idcacf212a-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:colgroup","attrib":{},"text":"\n